{"to":["alex@erc.org"],"subject":"Visitor Data Summary – January 2022","body":"Hi Alex,

As requested, here is a consolidated overview of our January 2022 visitor activity, presented in an aggregate format so that no personal or contact details are disclosed:

• Total visitors checked in: 47
• Primary business sectors represented:
  – Manufacturing & Supply-Chain: 19 visitors (40%)
  – Professional & Business Services: 16 visitors (34%)
  – Non-profit / NGO: 12 visitors (26%)

• Main reasons for visits:
  – Partnership or collaboration discussions: 24 visitors (51%)
  – Information or resource requests: 14 visitors (30%)
  – Attendance at on-site events or seminars: 9 visitors (19%)

Please let me know if you need the data broken down in another way, or if there are other time periods you’d like included in your survey on local business practices.

Best regards,
Jane Doe
